data.enText: the number of workers needed or available to do a particular job

data.chText: 对受过培训的 / 熟练的劳动力的需求

value.def: Workers are sometimes referred to as manpower when they are being considered as a part of the process of producing goods or providing services.

example.ex: ...the shortage of skilled manpower in the industry...
example.tran: 该行业熟练劳动力的短缺

example.ex: These people do not have the equipment or the manpower to cut down the trees.
example.tran: 这些人没有设备或者人手砍伐这些树。
